quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  5,10,"∆Āen yeddu…ďe …ďe fenni Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ďen …óon, ko yim…ďe Jahiimi"
  5,11,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, jantee Neema Alla on e dow moo…óon tuma nde yim…ďe himmirnoo nde …ďe fontata e dow moo…óon juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, Alla Suri juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen gaay e moo…óon. Hulee Alla. Ko e Alla gom…óim…ďe …ďen yowitotoo"
  5,12,"Gom…óii Alla Nanngi ahadi …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen, Men Immini e ma…ď…ďe gori sappo e …ói…ói. Allaahu On Daali : \"Min Mi…óo Wonndi e moo…óon : si on √Īii…ďnii julde nden, on jonnii asakal ngal, on gom…óinii Nulaa…ďe Am …ďen, o teddinii …ďe, on √Īawlii Alla √Īamaande mo∆ī∆īunde, Ma Mi heefan on bon…ói mon …óin, Ma Mi Naadoy on Aljannaaji …ói no ila e ley majji can…ói. Kala on yeddu…óo e moo…óon …ďaawo …óum, gom…óii on majjii laawol fotondirngol ngol\". @Corrected"
  5,13,"Ko sabu firtugol ma…ď…ďe ahadi ma…ď…ďe ndin Men Hu…óirnoo …ďe, Men Wa…ói …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen yooru…óe : hi…ďe waylita konngol ngol gaay e nokku maggol, …ďe yejjiti ge…ďal e kon ko …ďe anndintinanoo e mun. A seerataa hi…óa ∆īellitoo e dow janfa iwruka e ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa see…óaa…ďe e ma…ď…ďe.Yaafano …ďe laa…ďanaa […ďe]. Pellet, Alla no Yi…ói mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen"
